targets.queryText: select count(*) from tablescan;
targets.rawQueryText: select count(*) from tablescan;

targets.queryText: select drive_letter ,count(*) as file_num ,SUM(file_size)/1024/1024/1024 as `filesize(G)` from tablescan group by drive_letter
targets.rawQueryText: select drive_letter ,count(*) as file_num ,SUM(file_size)/1024/1024/1024 as `filesize(G)` from tablescan group by drive_letter

panels.title: The total number of files per drive letter

targets.queryText:
select a.drive_letter  ,a.file_name  ,a.file_modified_time  from tablescan a,(select drive_letter,max(file_modified_time) as lasttime from tablescan group by drive_letter) b 
where a.drive_letter=b.drive_letter and a.file_modified_time=b.lasttime order by a.drive_letter
targets.rawQueryText:
select a.drive_letter  ,a.file_name  ,a.file_modified_time  from tablescan a,(select drive_letter,max(file_modified_time) as lasttime from tablescan group by drive_letter) b 
where a.drive_letter=b.drive_letter and a.file_modified_time=b.lasttime order by a.drive_letter

panels.title: The latest file under each drive letter

targets.queryText:
select  case when first_level_directory='' then drive_letter else first_level_directory end as first_level_directory_path,
sum(file_size)/1024/1024 as `filesize_M` 
from tablescan group by  first_level_directory order by sum(file_size) desc
targets.rawQueryText:
select  case when first_level_directory='' then drive_letter else first_level_directory end as first_level_directory_path,
sum(file_size)/1024/1024 as `filesize_M` 
from tablescan group by  first_level_directory order by sum(file_size) desc

panels.title: Count file size for the first level directory below each drive letter

targets.queryText: select drive_letter,sum(file_size)/1024/1024/1024 as `Disk Used Size(G)`,count(*) as `Total number of disk files` from tablescan group by drive_letter
targets.rawQueryText: select drive_letter,sum(file_size)/1024/1024/1024 as `Disk Used Size(G)`,count(*) as `Total number of disk files` from tablescan group by drive_letter

targets.queryText: select file_extension as 文件扩展名,count(*) as 统计个数 from tablescan group by file_extension order by file_extension
targets.rawQueryText: select file_extension as 文件扩展名,count(*) as 统计个数 from tablescan group by file_extension order by file_extension
